  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492900/extras/59f4e3a8beb73a7ae78a0e36c5178742.poster.avif?t=1616161502\" width=770 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492900/extras/59f4e3a8beb73a7ae78a0e36c5178742.webm?t=1616161502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492900/extras/59f4e3a8beb73a7ae78a0e36c5178742.mp4?t=1616161502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Alien Trials</strong> is an action packed 1v1 fighting game. The rules are simple. Win the duel by successfully knocking out your foe. Play as an extraterrestrial in the ultimate brawl for survival!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Online Multiplayer </strong>- Host/Join matches online to showcase your true skill level or invite & play with friends.<br></li><li><strong>Training</strong> - Not ready for online play? Train your combat skills here with multiple AI modes.<br></li><li><strong>Unique Attacks & Movement Skills</strong> - Different options to take on your enemy. Discover combos that work well with your playstyle.<br></li><li>I<strong>mmersive Combat</strong> - Multiple visual and audio cues to fuel every punch or kick as you inch closer to victory.</li></ul></h2></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492900/extras/59f4e3a8beb73a7ae78a0e36c5178742.poster.avif?t=1616161502\" width=770 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492900/extras/59f4e3a8beb73a7ae78a0e36c5178742.webm?t=1616161502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492900/extras/59f4e3a8beb73a7ae78a0e36c5178742.mp4?t=1616161502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The Alien Trials</strong> is an action packed 1v1 fighting game. The rules are simple. Win the duel by successfully knocking out your foe. Play as an extraterrestrial in the ultimate brawl for survival!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Online Multiplayer </strong>- Host/Join matches online to showcase your true skill level or invite & play with friends.<br></li><li><strong>Training</strong> - Not ready for online play? Train your combat skills here with multiple AI modes.<br></li><li><strong>Unique Attacks & Movement Skills</strong> - Different options to take on your enemy. Discover combos that work well with your playstyle.<br></li><li>I<strong>mmersive Combat</strong> - Multiple visual and audio cues to fuel every punch or kick as you inch closer to victory.</li></ul></h2></h2>",
